She looked at Megatron. Her face showed fear towards him.
"Commander, there was a strange ship at our boarders.  I sent KitKat 
out to meet with it.  She is bringing back another bot to follow 
under your commander."  She tried to stand up and look proud for what 
she had said.  But feared Megatron's anger.
